com.conceptwave.scripting
Class FileWriter

com.conceptwave.scripting.Object
  com.conceptwave.scripting.CWScriptable
      com.conceptwave.scripting.FileWriter

public class FileWriter
extends CWScriptable

Output file manipulation class. Construction of a FileWriter is done as follows: new FileWriter(filename,append) where filename is the filename to create and write, and append is an optional parameter that indicates that the file is to be appended to (defaults to false). If a null filename is passed a unique filename prefixed by "cwf" is generated (directory path is the system temp directory). An I/O exception may occur the directory path in the filename does not exist.
